  <h2>HTML5 Front-end</h2>

  <p>
    Cascading Media employs nothing less than the most advanced front-end standards
    such as HTML5, Sass (CSS3)
    and the ES6 (ECMAScript 6) implementation of JavaScript
    for all sites and web applications we build.
    We leverage only the best front-end code libraries like
