    tablet computers
    and smart phones.
  </p>

  <p>
    We are asked about Adobe Flash from time to time
    and our policy is simple &#8211;
    Flash has no business on modern websites
    due to its poor compatibility with mobile devices,
    various security issues
    and the fact it has been rendered obsolete
    by HTML5 and related technologies.
  </p>

