  <h2>Ruby Back-end</h2>

  <p>
    For applications that require dynamic web pages and database interactions,
    Cascading Media&#8217;s programing language of choice is
    <a href="https://www.ruby-lang.org" target="_blank">Ruby</a>.
    Ruby is a powerful programming language with a focus on simplicity and productivity.
